Nengi has accused her closest Housemate, Ozo, of masturbating after claiming to see semen stains on his duvet. The current Head of House said this while on Ozo’s bed. “Ozo there are semen stains on your bed,” she said. Ozo however denied saying “Anything you see here is from the laundry. This place is too small for such a thing.” Replying, Nengi said: “It’s a lie. Who was talking about it the other day, was it Praise or who? That you can just be doing your thing… tell me, have you tried it before? “Those stains I saw under your bed, I’m suspecting you. You have tried it in this House. You have tried it. Don’t tell me lies, you’ve tried it. If you haven’t you would’ve told me.” On her part, Nengi said she tried masturbating but it didn’t work.